!! [[0.9.5|https://crosseye.github.io/TW5-JSON_Convert/0.9.5/]]
//Released 2026-05-16//

Per-release changelog system and pass-through picker polish.

* Per-version Changelog system: each release is its own tiddler tagged `$:/tags/json-convert/version`; the [[Changelog]] tiddler aggregates them in reverse-chronological order
* Retroactive demo builds for every prior release (v0.1.0–v0.8.0 plus v0.5.1, v0.9.0, v0.9.1), now reachable at `https://crosseye.github.io/TW5-JSON_Convert/<version>/`
* Pass-through picker: checkbox column right-aligned (checkbox now renders after the name input, so all checkboxes line up vertically regardless of name length)
* CI: `latest.yml` and `release.yml` workflows hardened against the concurrent-push race between them
